text: Frank James Sensenbrenner Jr. (; born June 14, 1943) is an American politician. He represented in the United States House of Representatives from 1979 to 2021. He is a Republican. Sensenbrenner announced in September 2019 that he would not run for re-election in 2020. ==References== Category:1943 births Category:Living people Category:United States representatives from Wisconsin Category:Republican Party (United States) politicians Category:Politicians from Chicago Category:Politicians from Milwaukee Category:Lawyers from Milwaukee Category:Lawyers from Chicago
